---
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-28 px-6 section-animate" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Section label -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-32">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="font-mono text-[#00e5c8]/60 text-xs tracking-widest">02.</span>
            <span class="w-8 h-px bg-[#00e5c8]/40"></span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white mb-6">About<br/>Me</h2>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/40">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00e5c8]"></span>
              <span class="font-mono">Available for work</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/40">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>
              <span class="font-mono">Remote / Hybrid</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-9 space-y-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          My journey into DevOps began with a passion for automation and building reliable infrastructure.
          I transitioned from traditional development to focus on the critical aspects of modern software delivery:
          automating processes, establishing CI/CD pipelines, and containerizing applications.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          What drives my work is the pursuit of efficiency and reliability. I specialize in using
          <span class="text-white font-medium">Infrastructure as Code</span> (primarily Terraform) to provision cloud resources,
          implementing <span class="text-white font-medium">Kubernetes</span> for orchestration, and designing
          CI/CD pipelines that enable teams to deploy with confidence.
        </p>

        <!-- Highlighted quote -->
        <div class="relative pl-6 py-6 border-l-2 border-[#00e5c8]">
          <div class="absolute -left-1 top-6 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#00e5c8] shadow-[0_0_10px_#00e5c8]"></div>
          <p class="text-xl text-white font-medium leading-relaxed italic">
            "Committed to continuous learning, staying current with cloud technologies, and sharing knowledge with the community."
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          I believe in the philosophy of continuous improvement—both in infrastructure and in my own growth as an engineer.
          Whether it's exploring new tools, improving system performance, or mentoring others, I'm always looking for ways
          to elevate my craft.
        </p>

        <!-- Skills row -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4 pt-4">
          {['Terraform', 'Kubernetes', 'AWS', 'Docker', 'CI/CD', 'GitOps', 'Helm', 'Linux'].map(skill => (
            <div class="px-4 py-2.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-center">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm text-white/70">{skill}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
